Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱之后是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是之前不是才增加过人手的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完全不考虑人工费的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  确实是增加人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是在特定的几个部门而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他地方还是不够
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说需要招聘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能顺利招聘到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定有才能的美少女会相继来应聘的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我肯定会身体前倾的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会有威胁到五十铃小姐地位的应聘者出现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个人比我更有才能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐意把现在的工作交给她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃小姐  我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  明天开始招聘工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可儿江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望从事的工作是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们全都录用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:02:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真正的压迫面试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三重压迫面试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么千斗  你还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord1\blur3\3a&H80\pos(1050,715)}{\fad(500,1000)}人手不足!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会做那种梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挫折的话  我也不输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了多招到一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我会不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然害怕起高处了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会有人吃这里的咖喱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  马卡隆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要吃那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上总觉得想试试这种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  不过小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前瓦尼皮吃了之后  上吐下泻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以坐这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上就吃咖喱  会胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃妹妹一直都是一个人吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这样  五十铃妹妹你不擅长跟人相处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是想得太多所以说不出来那种类型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是可儿江君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  千斗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做了个噩梦  吃了份难吃的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被同事各种抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作上也是各种不顺心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很辛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在辅佐可儿江同学的立场上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不确信自己是否能回应他的期待  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可儿江同学怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  千斗同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  摆造型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了西尔菲之外都不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让五十铃妹妹吃了真话果实?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混在咖喱里让她吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是马卡隆你说想知道女儿的真实想法我才给的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想从离婚的妻子那里把女儿的养育权夺回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然想夺回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以给女儿吃之前先让五十铃妹妹试试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在五十铃妹妹肯定藏不住真话正困扰着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过确认效果之前  五十铃妹妹就去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想问问她一周自己玩几次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是问了这个  之后会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就干掉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fn@方正准圆_GBK\c&H060A7B&\pos(804,260)\frz297.563}犯人是乳袋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs34}乳袋：动漫业特指衣物能紧贴胸部曲线（特别是下半部分）的效果。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃了真话果实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后想问我下流的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下流的问题?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周自己玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太懂  不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把躺在那边的笨蛋们叫起来之后来办公楼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13点开始面试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面  面试…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题大了去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是藏不住真话的状态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出点意外  把对你的不明感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要请病假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我对你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神这么好  看来没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  别迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fn@方正兰亭准黑_GBK\frz-90\an7\pos(870,84)\fsp10\c&H918F8F&}甘城光辉游乐园\N{\fscy160}\h{\fscy100}\N{\fs30}{\fscx1150}\h{\fscx100\c&H777571&}职员\N{\fscy180}\h{\fscy100}\N{\fs50\fsp10}{\fscx350}\h{\fscx100\c&H929590&}面试会场\N{\fscy285}\h{\fscy100}\N{\fs36\fscx860}\h{\fscx100\c&H9C9990&}理\N{\fscx860}\h{\fscx100}受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的市长选举落选了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:09:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想在这里东山再起  接下来去竞选总理大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真顽强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  录用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顽强的人才能坚持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是在最后一局没有暴投的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该不是应聘动机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中球员的眼泪让人感动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  录用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职员需要给来宾带来感动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被职业摔跤开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小就很懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别不喜欢向对方施展摔跤技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想啊  很疼很可怜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要去当职业摔跤手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具男我们已经有一个警卫部的奥库罗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色重了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意的是那方面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  把面具摘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格变了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟游乐园里的角色重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其摘掉面具  我不如去死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫奥库罗来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能向对方施展摔跤技的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是职业摔跤手的本能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个游乐园的人手不足已经到这个程度了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说严重啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来自伊贺的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我的生命全部献给主公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是蓝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫安达映子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好普通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能有个正常的面试了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦成真…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  安达映子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是在艺人事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出演过电影作品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出演过什么样的电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是AV
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出演过AV
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  做了很长时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太长  也就出演了10部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10部…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问问她的艺名  超在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问得出来才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是很少见的经历  有点动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家经常这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要在意  我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面试官失敬是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧问她艺名和出道作品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千斗  要怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可儿江同学  请不要依赖我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在十分困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个女人跟我梦中出现的应聘者一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有可儿江同学听了她的履历非常动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种巨乳大姐姐的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着我没有的包容力以及超丰富的性经验
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这种女人让我感到自愧不如
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道想让她当秘书  把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么想来这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安达小姐是为什么想来这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的工作好像不太适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过我还是想亲眼看到客人们开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问这样不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得这个理由很伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把安达映子的照片发给特利戈让他帮我查查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙对AV很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚯嚯  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  叫下一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  那个…映子小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的艺名已经查到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫伴藤美衣乃  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦又成真了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有精神  不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…伴藤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个的血迹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为我急着过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  这只是擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是刺伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失血量大概是1升左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这次面试我上赌上了一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要把命也赌上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到被录用为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  录用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被录用了  所以拜托你快上救护车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他反对我打工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是为了不让我来面试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么家庭环境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  录用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时只能吃流食了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形势所迫就把那女孩录用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一般来说是不应该录用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她即使被刺也能维持责任感和笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这份热情和毅力  说不定能成为游乐园的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得你说的很有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么有看人的眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不反映在行动上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样胸部才这么大的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…梦里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从刚才起到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是最后的应聘者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身校服  甘城高中?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我叫中条椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应聘的是…这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性应聘者很少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她这个样子的话  诱惑你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个性格去接客想必会很困难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你会反对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了之前那帮家伙就觉得无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  中条椎菜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被录用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就是最后的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上马卡隆说我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得太多所以说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对面的时候我会不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才掏枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只要退一步就能冷静看待的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,评价一个人和接触一个人是完全不同的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别纠结了  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算是在鼓励我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓励?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁鼓励谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很多方面  我都很嫉妒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会嫉妒我是很正常的  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可儿江同学  你那极度傲慢居高临下的态度不能改改吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在高处是事实  没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神莉布拉  请给这个男人带去灾难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千斗吗
