Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是Animal  Video?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员列队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来到了这里  你们就不再是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是地上最卑劣的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你们能正常接客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会以最严厉的方面锻炼你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的挫折和掉队就是我们的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  菜鸟们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话的前后要加上Sir  知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir  是  Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Sir  Yes  Sir
